captions.text: (Music)

Trick camera, all of those shots, it had
to be. And the first two, hitting the
crossbar from the halfway line.
Number one…is accuracy.
Number two…is consistency, right?
Trick camera, trick camera, trick camera.
Hey Lassi, help me!
Yeah, I think the majority are all fake.

and the fact that he is driving with his
phone, I think that's illegal anyway so he
should be getting into trouble.
Fake, fake, fake.

Do you remember that football you
borrowed me?

Well it sucks, do you still
want it back? No? Sounds good.

Lassi, have you ever thought of a video
with Remi [Gaillard]?
Absolutely.

KICKTV actually contacted him but he
said my videos were fake.

So I don't know if we would do
something together.

If you could send him a message,
what would you say?

My videos are all real. They are just
done with Finnish "Sisu."
And what is that?

"Sisu" is a term or an expression which
means strength of will,
patience, and determination.
So, Monseigneur Gaillard,
Anytime, any place…your move.
